column4: why does bzr branch ubuntu:<package> download quantal and not precise?
because it is the current dev version, if you want precise, bzr branch lp:ubuntu/precise/package
though the branches are kind of all over the place so you may not necessarily get what you want there
aye, makes sense though dev version is what's usually needed when fetching source not current stable
